    "en": {
      "title": "The body of the student was recovered after 4 days",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The body of a student of Peradanai University, who committed suicide by jumping into the Mahavali River from the Peradanai Bridge, was recovered today (31) during the day.",
        "The 24-year-old from Belmadulla, who was studying in the 3rd year of the Faculty of Engineering of Peradanai University, jumped into the river from the Peradanai bridge on the evening of the 27th.",
        "The cause of death of the deceased student is yet to be ascertained and the Peradana police have said that investigations are being carried out in this regard."
      ],
